entry.summary:
Cobrowse.io - iOS Native SDK

Cobrowse.io - iOS Native SDK

Cobrowse.io is 100% free and easy to try out in your own apps.

Register an account at https://cobrowse.io/register.

Please see full documentation at https://docs.cobrowse.io.

Try our online demo at https://cobrowse.io/demo.

Installation

See the installation documentation to get started.

Try it out

Once you have your app running in the iOS Simulator or on a physical device, navigate to https://cobrowse.io/dashboard to see your device listed. You can click the "Connect" button to initiate a Cobrowse session!

Optional features

Identify your devices

Use 6-digit codes

Redact sensitive data

Customize the interface

Initiate sessions with push

Full device capabilities

Advanced features

Questions?

Any questions at all? Please email us directly at hello@cobrowse.io.

Requirements

  • iOS 11.0 or later
